msgctxt "84_Angry Man"
msgid "I fulfilled all his requirements, I know I did! So why won't\\r\n"\n"he lend me my money? What does he want from me?"
msgstr "¡Cumplo con todos sus requisitos, eso lo tengo claro! ¿Por qué\\r\n"\n"no me presta dinero? ¿Qué más quiere de mí?"

msgctxt "96_Angry Man"
msgid "Those rumors about Sky Finance were nothing but a pack of\\r\n"\n"lies! That bastard Akiyama... He won't get away with\\r\n"\n"this!"
msgstr "¡Esos rumores sobre el Sky Finance no son más que puras\\r\n"\n"mentiras! Ese maldito Akiyama... ¡No se saldrá con\\r\n"\n"la suya!"

msgctxt "108_Akiyama"
msgid "(Huh? He's talking about me. I don't remember ever seeing him before, though.)"
msgstr "(¿Eh? Está hablando de mí. Pero no recuerdo haberlo visto antes)"

msgctxt "120_Akiyama"
msgid "Excuse me, did I hear you say something about Sky Finance\\r\n"\n"just now?"
msgstr "Disculpa, ¿has dicho algo sobre Sky Finance\\r\n"\n"hace un momento?"

msgctxt "132_Angry Man"
msgid "What's it to you, pal? Beat it!"
msgstr "¿Qué quieres, compadre? ¡Lárgate!"

msgctxt "144_Akiyama"
msgid "Well, it's just that Sky Finance－"
msgstr "Bueno, es solo que el Sky Finance －"

msgctxt "156_Angry Man"
msgid "Didn't I tell you to beat it? I don't have time for this\\r\n"\n"crap!"
msgstr "¿No te he dicho que te largues? ¡No tengo tiempo para tus\\r\n"\n"estupideces!"

msgctxt "168_Akiyama"
msgid "Okay, okay!"
msgstr "¡Vale, vale!"

msgctxt "180_Akiyama"
msgid "(Wish I could hear more, but this joker won't give me the time of day...)"
msgstr "(Ojalá hubiera escuchado más, pero este payaso no me dirá ni la hora...)"

